  <p>Break-Even Volume is the monthly output token count where self-hosting becomes cheaper than API.</p>
  <p>Quality Gap is approximate and task-dependent. Benchmarks like MMLU, HumanEval, and GPQA inform these estimates.</p>
  <p>Some links may include referral codes.</p>
